      &lt;h2 class=&quot;my-0 mb-[16px] text-ellipsis text-[18px] font-medium text-emphasis&quot;&gt;
        延伸阅读
      &lt;/h2&gt;
      
          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20250417-6203416&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              下午察：敦煌网在美爆红 是流量奇迹还是一时狂欢？
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
